

 Some mongo directories to consider 
===================================


/var/lib/mongodb
/var/log/mongodb
/etc/mongod.conf

Start    : sudo systemctl start mongod
Status   : sudo systemctl status mongod
Stop     : sudo systemctl stop mongod
Restart  : sudo systemctl restart mongod

Bootime ON : 
========================

